---
title: Smart Vietnamese-Style Marinated Tofu with Fresh Salad and Shallots
description: Easier than takeout and as fresh as can be, this dinner delivers big, bold South-East Asian flavours of chili, cilantro, fried shallots, garlic and soy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-marine-a-la-vietnamienne-9fcb08a7.jpg
